      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CLASSIC BOODIE (3) is a consistent runner who is new here. Comes here an impressive winner latest at Q Lakeside in Grade 5 in one of the quickest times of the program (19.76). Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Can continue on with her winning form. GINGER BELLE (2) took the sit on the lead from an outside box but levelled up and drew clear to score (20.25) at this track in a Maiden over 350m. The form out of her last race has been franked. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. COSMIC CASPER (1) pinged the lids and was in the firing line throughout but drifted out of it when 8th at this track in a Grade 5. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. One of the main contenders. CONFETTI DAN (4) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance - should be thereabouts.",
